Class PHIImportBuilder<T extends PHIImportBuilder<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openehealth.ipf.commons.audit.event.DelegatingAuditMessageBuilder<T,D>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AuditMessageBuilder<T>, Validateable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    XdsPHIImportBuilder

    public class PHIImportBuilder<T extends PHIImportBuilder<T>>
extends IHEAuditMessageBuilder<T,DataImportBuilder>
    Builder for building IHE-specific DataImport events. It automatically sets the AuditSource, local and remote ActiveParticipant and a Human Requestor and provides methods for adding patient IDs.
    Since:
    3.5
    Author:
